content.title: The title of hyperlink builder should be 'Hyperlink Options', now it changes with settings.
content.OB: When clicking on 'OK' and then reopening the hyperlink builder, its title becomes 'www.actuate.com'.
content.EB: The title of the hyperlink builder should always be 'Hyperlink Options'.
content.SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Set a label hyperlink as 'www.actuate.com'.
2. Click on 'OK', then reopen the hyperlink builder.
